DEFINE
	VAR __H0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS(
			{(2146554936592, "Bitcoin")},
			'cleaned_crypto_data'[Market Cap (USD)],
			'cleaned_crypto_data'[Coin Name]
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'cleaned_crypto_data'[Volume Tier],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('cleaned_crypto_data'[Continent], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			"CountCoin_Name", CALCULATE(COUNTA('cleaned_crypto_data'[Coin Name])),
			"cleaned_crypto_dataCountCoin_Name", IGNORE(
				CALCULATE(COUNTA('cleaned_crypto_data'[Coin Name]), KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable))
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'cleaned_crypto_data'[Volume Tier]", 'cleaned_crypto_data'[Volume Tier],
			"'cleaned_crypto_data'[Continent]", 'cleaned_crypto_data'[Continent],
			"CountCoin_Name", [CountCoin_Name],
			"cleaned_crypto_dataCountCoin_Name", [cleaned_crypto_dataCountCoin_Name]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'cleaned_crypto_data'[Volume Tier]", 'cleaned_crypto_data'[Volume Tier],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [CountCoin_Name]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'cleaned_crypto_data'[Volume Tier]),
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			201,
			__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
			[SortBy_DM0_0],
			0,
			'cleaned_crypto_data'[Volume Tier],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'cleaned_crypto_data'[Continent])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'cleaned_crypto_data'[Continent], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'cleaned_crypto_data'[Continent],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'cleaned_crypto_data'[Continent]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'cleaned_crypto_data'[Volume Tier], [ColumnIndex]
